<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.5.5">
<l>karumaka ḷilaṅkai yāṭṭi pilaṅkoḷvāy tiṟantu taṉmēl</l>
<l>varumavaḷ ceviyum mūkkum vāḷiṉāl taṭinta ventai</l>
<l>perumakaḷ pētai maṅkai taṉṉoṭum pirivi lāta</l>
<l>tirumakaḷ maruvum nāṅkūrt tirumaṇik kūṭat taṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Our father who with a sword hacked off the nose and ears of the dark woman,</l>
<l>The lady of  Lanka who came at him, opening her cavernous mouth,</l>
<l>Is the one in Tirumaṇikkūṭam in Nāṅkūr who embraces the great lady,</l>
<l>The simple lady, and Tiru who is inseparable from him.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
